NBC May Broadcast All Three Races in Triple Crown, CNBC Says

-- B y   N a d i n e   S k o c z y l a s
-- 
2011-02-22T14:18:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-22/nbc-may-broadcast-all-three-races-in-triple-crown-horse-racing-cnbc-says.html
NBC Sports Group may announce today
plans to acquire rights to broadcast all three races in the
Triple Crown: the Kentucky Derby, Preakness and Belmont, CNBC
reported, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nadine Skoczylas at 
 nelsibai@bloomberg.net  